1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,300
Episode 58

2
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:06,700
No need to follow. I will serve her.

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,300
Understood.

4
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:16,300
Speak your mind.

5
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,100
She was only pretending to be nice just now,

6
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:19,700
don't tell me you are willing to trust her again!

7
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:21,000
Why shouldn't I believe her?

8
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,700
I saw clearly just now

9
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:24,100
insider her satchel was--

10
00:00:24,371 --> 00:00:26,984
If you know what's in her satchel

11
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,300
then you must also know what she intends to do.

12
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:35,500
What she said today may not have all been false,

13
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:38,500
there is a semblance of truth.

14
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,500
Jin Xi,

15
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,700
Niang niang.

16
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,100
You saw Su Peisheng, what did he say?

17
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:49,700
What did he say?

18
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:50,900
He said,

19
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,600
Qi Pin and An Pin

20
00:00:52,608 --> 00:00:54,142
are now in the Empress's camp.

21
00:00:54,193 --> 00:00:57,086
But they have only ever been friends for show.

22
00:00:57,126 --> 00:01:00,147
Lately the Empress favours Qi Pin,

23
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,900
An Pin can't help but feel neglected.

24
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:07,400
Qi Pin is shallow and loves to flaunt

25
00:01:08,282 --> 00:01:09,613
If I was the Empress,

26
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:12,400
I would also view her as the more controllable one.

27
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,900
An Ling-Rong is vicious and skilled at manipulation

28
00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:18,000
She and the Empress are of the same persuasion.

29
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,600
Most likely not even the Empress

30
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,600
can fully control her.

31
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:25,200
These infidels are in league with each other<br>(Lit. A den of snakes and mice)

32
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,000
but still can't keep away from internal strife.

33
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:28,000
Serves them right.

34
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:31,300
Young Mistress, what do you plan to do?

35
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,500
Since An Ling Rong came specifically to inform

36
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,600
I may as well accept her gift.

37
00:01:37,676 --> 00:01:38,632
Huan Bi,

38
00:01:39,241 --> 00:01:40,292
Go tell Pei Er

39
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:42,000
let Xin Guiren know.

40
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:43,000
Understood.

41
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:49,700
Consort, <br> His majesty is coming tonight

42
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,000
Should we start preparing?

43
00:01:52,512 --> 00:01:53,876
Prepare for what?

44
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:58,000
Xiao Yun-Zi told me earlier that

45
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:01,100
the Princess was very unaccustomed to you.

46
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:03,400
It's understandable that you are angry with His Majesty.

47
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:06,700
He is the culprit.

48
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,500
Your Majesty, please have some lotus seed soup

49
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:17,900
it's especially good for the summer heat.

50
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,100
Have you sent someone to Consort Xi?

51
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,800
Is she feeling better?

52
00:02:24,100 --> 00:02:25,700
Still the same,

53
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,800
melancholic as always.

54
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:32,000
Your Majesty, even if Xi Fei Niangniang can take it

55
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,300
bear it,

56
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,700
the child in her can't.

57
00:02:35,349 --> 00:02:37,116
I am not settled either.

58
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:40,500
Arrange for some entertaining performances

59
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,300
to cheer her up.

60
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:45,900
But Your Majesty, that's not what Niangniang desires the most

61
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,300
It won't be effective.

62
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,900
She will not be happy.

63
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,500
Then, what do you suggest I do?

64
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,600
Niangniang is alone in the palace and must miss her family,

65
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,100
but the Princess won't be close with her,

66
00:02:56,204 --> 00:02:59,344
Your Majesty, why not arrange for a meeting with her other family members?

67
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,900
Perhaps seeing them will cheer her and disperse her unhappiness

68
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:03,200
then she may get better.

69
00:03:05,471 --> 00:03:07,083
I know what to do.

70
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,400
Zhen Yuan-Dao hasn't yet fully recovered from his illness,

71
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,700
I am afraid he might infect Xi Fei if they meet.

72
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:16,500
I will naturally allow them a meeting

73
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,700
when Zhen Yuan-Dao has recovered.

74
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:19,700
Yes, Your Majesty.

75
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:26,700
His Majesty has arrived.

76
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,800
Greetings, Your Majesty.

77
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:31,700
Rise.

78
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,245
Thank you, Your Majesty.

79
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,700
You are finally feeling better today?

80
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,500
Thank you, Your Majesty.

81
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,600
Su Gonggong said

82
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:49,300
Your Majesty has permitted my father to visit me after he recovers.

83
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,400
I feel much better hearing that.

84
00:03:52,276 --> 00:03:54,278
Right now I have no other wish than

85
00:03:54,328 --> 00:03:56,525
for my family to be safe and sound

86
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:59,500
and to give Your Majesty a son.

87
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:02,600
Niangniang's family is also His Majesty's family,

88
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,500
they are important to Him too.

89
00:04:04,951 --> 00:04:06,590
Niangniang can rest assured.

90
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:10,700
Your Majesty, Jing Shi Fang inquired earlier

91
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:13,600
whether you would like to flip a card tonight.

92
00:04:13,947 --> 00:04:16,278
No need, I will stay here.

93
00:04:16,363 --> 00:04:17,322
Yes.

94
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:19,700
You Majesty, have you forgotten the imperial doctor's advice again?

95
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:22,000
It is good just to be in your company.

96
00:04:22,695 --> 00:04:24,811
I wouldn't want Your Majesty to feel denied,

97
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,400
and ask that Your Majesty not tease me either.

98
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:29,200
It's probably best to go elsewhere.

99
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,000
Then...

100
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,400
Chun Xi Dian.

101
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,600
Yes.

102
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:39,300
I will go and inform Ning Guiren to prepare.

103
00:04:39,917 --> 00:04:42,866
But Qi Pin will be muttering again

104
00:04:42,918 --> 00:04:45,489
when I pass by Chu Xiu Gong.

105
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:50,100
Oh? Do they often gossip about my attentiveness to Ning Guiren?

106
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:50,400
That I love Lady Ning too much?

107
00:04:50,614 --> 00:04:51,948
I can't say often,

108
00:04:51,962 --> 00:04:54,981
I just happened to overhear a few times.

109
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,100
You can't really blame Qi Pin.

110
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,000
The Empress Dowager isn't fond of Ning Guiren,

111
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:00,700
much less the others.

112
00:05:00,895 --> 00:05:02,286
The Empress Dowager is the Empress Dowager.

113
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,100
Who does she think she is?

114
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,500
Qi Pin is only jealous.

115
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:10,000
It's such a hot day, please do not let anger affect your health.

116
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,100
Your Majesty,

117
00:05:14,641 --> 00:05:17,378
Chu Xiu Gong sent someone to say that Qi Pin feels unwell

118
00:05:17,405 --> 00:05:19,546
will Your Majesty visit her?

119
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:23,700
If she's unwell then send for a doctor, do I know how to cure her?

120
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:30,600
Foolish thing!

121
00:05:30,611 --> 00:05:32,337
Tell her I'm busy.

122
00:05:32,447 --> 00:05:33,635
Understood.

123
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,900
I didn't know Your Majesty had such a penchant for bluffing.

124
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:41,100
She loves to whine, I don't want to deal with her right now.

125
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,400
If you don't want to see her then don't,

126
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:45,000
why tell me about it?

127
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:48,300
As if I'm to blame.

128
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:50,600
Of course you're to blame.

129
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:53,200
If you were a bit more foolish,

130
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:55,200
more ugly,

131
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,600
less gentle, understanding

132
00:05:57,630 --> 00:06:00,180
then I might like her more.

133
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:03,100
Everybody says to treat new affections and old loves equally,

134
00:06:03,421 --> 00:06:05,292
Why is Your Majesty alone so partial?

135
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,800
Qi Pin can be a little difficult as times

136
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:10,000
but she is not one to claim illness without reason.

137
00:06:10,039 --> 00:06:12,056
Why not check on her?

138
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:15,300
I will accompany you, <br> Think of it as a stroll.

139
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,900
Who says His Majesty won't come see me?

140
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:21,800
It's all because of you grovelling mongrels

141
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:25,000
trying to degrade me to suck up to Yong Shou Gong.

142
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,000
Audacious!<br>Your Majesty, be careful!

143
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:38,500
His Majesty is here!

144
00:06:38,867 --> 00:06:41,061
Greetings, Your Majesty.

145
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,300
Greetings, Your Majesty.

146
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:47,900
Didn't you say you were ill?

147
00:06:48,211 --> 00:06:50,311
You look very well to me.

148
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:54,300
Thank you for your concern Your Majesty,

149
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:56,600
I was just disciplining the servants,

150
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:58,600
I really am ill.

151
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:02,200
Ill? Instead of resting, you're hitting your servant.

152
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:05,000
What wrong has she committed for you to punish her so severely?

153
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,700
She disrespected me and defied my authority,

154
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:10,500
I only hit her a little because she made me excessively angry.

155
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,700
You speak.

156
00:07:11,993 --> 00:07:14,863
Qi Pin was hitting my maid, Pei Er.

157
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:18,100
Just now, she sent someone to invite Your Majesty, but the answer was no.

158
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:18,400
Therefore,

159
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:21,500
So she took her anger out on Pei Er.

160
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,000
Pei Er,

161
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,000
I am here.

162
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:30,500
Was it you who went to Yang Xin Dian to ask for me?

163
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:32,100
Your Majesty,

164
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,900
it was not me.

165
00:07:34,184 --> 00:07:36,365
It was Niangniang's servant Jing Tai who went.

166
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,400
She wasn't the one who asked for me,

167
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:40,200
why did you take your anger out on her?

168
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,000
I was-

169
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,200
It's because Pei Er used to serve Xi Fei

170
00:07:43,592 --> 00:07:45,969
Qi Pin has been resentful ever since

171
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:47,900
Xi Fei's pregnancy was announced.

172
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,500
Therefore, she would always hit me to vent her anger.

173
00:07:50,897 --> 00:07:52,498
How dare you slander me!

174
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:56,300
You. Raise your head.

175
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,800
Hm. You really did serve Xi Fei.

176
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:03,400
No wonder you were cursing Yong Shou Gong earlier.

177
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,200
I would not dare!

178
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,300
Flogging a servant innocent of crime,

179
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:09,300
absolutely no compassion.

180
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,600
Your jealousy over Xi Fei's pregnancy made you disrespect your superior.

181
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,700
Moreover, the anger you vented on servants over my absence

182
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:18,000
is really directed at me.

183
00:08:18,393 --> 00:08:20,649
Forgive me Your Majesty!

184
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:23,900
Your Majesty, please look.

185
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,900
Qi Pin takes every little thing out on Pei Er.

186
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,500
Look what she's done,

187
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,900
there's not one spot on Pei Er devoid of scars.

188
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,900
I am useless.

189
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,900
She always uses her higher position to rebuke me.

190
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:40,200
I can't even protect my own servants.

191
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:42,000
Pin? (Imperial Consort, 5th rank.)

192
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,400
Is this how the mistress of a palace should act?

193
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:52,500
Gua Er Jia (Qi Pin's family name),

194
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:55,400
insolent and contemptuous of authority,

195
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,800
She will be degraded to Lady.

196
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,200
Your Majesty.

197
00:08:59,472 --> 00:09:01,178
To be moved to Jiao Hu Guan (Lagoon Palace?).

198
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:03,700
Starting today, you are grounded.

199
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,500
You are not to step one foot outside without my order.

200
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,900
Xin Gui Ren will take charge of Chu Xiu Gong.

201
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,300
Thank you, Your majesty.

202
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,900
Your majesty, I'm begging you!

203
00:09:13,213 --> 00:09:14,541
Don't do this to me.

204
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,300
Greetings, Empress Dowager

205
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,100
Rise.

206
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,300
Thank you, Empress Dowager

207
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,400
Quickly

208
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,300
Your complexion looks better, Your Highness.

209
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,700
Everyday I have to drink so much bitter medicine,

210
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,500
so much that my face turns red.

211
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,500
So my complexion seems healthy even though I am not.

212
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,200
It's simply a façade.

213
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,100
Emperor,

214
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:43,800
Look at Xi Fei, she's too well behaved.

215
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:46,000
I've told her countless times

216
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:48,400
to dispense with palace etiquette during her pregnancy,

217
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,000
but she won't listen.

218
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:53,500
Xi Fei is as filial to you as I am.

219
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,000
It's inconvenient for a pregnant woman to travel, why did you come here?

220
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,500
Xi Fei's stomach looks

221
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:04,100
a little bigger than what one would expect for the fifth month.

222
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,400
The Imperial Doctor said

223
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,700
I have twins.

224
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,955
That's why it's bigger.

225
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:14,100
Huan Huan, truly?

226
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:17,600
Doctor Wen said so. I would not dare to deceive you.

227
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:20,900
Surely with Doctor Wen's skill a misdiagnosis is not likely.

228
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:26,200
Such a felicitous event,

229
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,800
I should proclaim it to the whole world!

230
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:33,100
I am already blessed with the opportunity to serve you once more.

231
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:34,700
I would not dare receive

232
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:37,400
the honour of a national proclamation, for the children in me.

233
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,400
I am not worthy of such grace.

234
00:10:40,674 --> 00:10:42,506
Xi Fei is very sensible.

235
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,100
I have only just returned to the Palace.

236
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,900
I would not provoke any disputes if possible,

237
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,400
and desire only to carry my children peacefully to term.

238
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,700
I wish to be undisturbed by those who seek to congratulate me.

239
00:10:53,185 --> 00:10:56,730
Therefore, I hope that the news about twins

240
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,800
will remain confidential

241
00:10:59,078 --> 00:11:00,946
until they are born.

242
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:06,900
The Harem's knowledge about this matter could indeed disturb Xi Fei's pregnancy.

243
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:11,200
They will find out

244
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,100
there is no hurry.

245
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:17,800
Mother, I have no objections since you and Xi Fei both feel this way.

246
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:20,500
Only,

247
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:22,900
it is such a pity

248
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:26,100
that no one can celebrate with us over so joyous a matter.

249
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:30,300
Your Majesty need not feel regret. <br>If the Imperial Doctor is indeed right, celebrations are inevitable.

250
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,800
Xi Fei is right.

251
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:35,400
But being pregnant with twins

252
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:38,100
will only inconvenience her more to serve you.

253
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,400
There are many consorts of good character

254
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,200
among Xi Fei's friends.

255
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:47,100
Why not let Xi Fei have a leisurely rest,

256
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:49,100
and let the other consorts serve you?

257
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,000
I personally feel

258
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:53,900
Hui Pin to be dignified and proper. She is a good choice.

259
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,300
Yes.

260
00:11:55,733 --> 00:11:58,338
I defer to your wisdom, Mother.

261
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:03,200
Also, the Empress may not be severely sick,

262
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,100
but the ailment refuses to leave her.

263
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:08,200
Why not task the Bureau of Astronomy to take a look

264
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:10,300
if anything is seriously wrong.

265
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:14,900
Then call on Baohua Temple to chant scriptures and pray for blessings.

266
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,100
Yes.

