00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:45,800
Greetings, Consort Xi.

540
00:31:45,907 --> 00:31:48,537
She is wet. Jin-Xi, give her a cloth.

541
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,400
Lady,

542
00:31:52,681 --> 00:31:54,314
don't catch a cold.

543
00:31:55,300 --> 00:31:56,900
Do you like Albizia flowers?

544
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:00,700
Why don't we ask the servant to cover the flowers?

545
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:03,800
They can send the flowers to you when the rain stops.

546
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,300
Then you won't have to do this in the rain.

547
00:32:06,637 --> 00:32:08,289
Thank you.

548
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:10,800
Spring is coming soon.

549
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:14,200
The albizia flowers are beginning to fade.

550
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:18,700
Among all the albizia flowers in the imperial garden, these are the prettiest.

551
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:22,100
That's not true.

552
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:24,700
The albizia flowers in House of Concentraing Glow are the best.

553
00:32:24,900 --> 00:32:27,200
You can smell the fragrance

554
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:30,000
every summer.

555
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,800
I have never seen it.

556
00:32:35,127 --> 00:32:37,475
I am of low birth,

557
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:39,800
that I can't even be compared to a servant.

558
00:32:40,122 --> 00:32:42,060
But I can wander where I like.

559
00:32:43,705 --> 00:32:45,728
You shouldn't

560
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,900
look down on yourself.

561
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:52,700
I am the daughter of a guilty officer too.

562
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,800
The rain is subsiding.

563
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:01,800
When you are out,

564
00:33:02,514 --> 00:33:05,841
do you want my servant to send you back when the rain stops?

565
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:09,300
No, Consort wants to go to Hall of Autumn Happiness.

566
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:12,500
Why would you go there?

567
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:14,800
Is it that you don't welcome me?

568
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,600
Greetings, Consort.

569
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,414
Greetings, Consort.

570
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:38,500
Have a seat.

571
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:49,300
Your cat is pretty.

572
00:33:49,547 --> 00:33:52,152
What's so special about it?

573
00:33:53,847 --> 00:33:54,988
Where is the cat?

574
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:06,900
This cat is quiet.

575
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:09,700
It is the most clever as well.

576
00:34:10,023 --> 00:34:11,714
Normally it doesn't meow.

577
00:34:12,100 --> 00:34:12,800
When it meows,

578
00:34:13,136 --> 00:34:15,547
the other cats come near here.

579
00:34:18,100 --> 00:34:19,500
Are you afraid of cats?

580
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,100
No.

581
00:34:21,200 --> 00:34:22,700
I am just curious.

582
00:34:22,807 --> 00:34:24,787
How did you manage to train it?

583
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:31,200
I was an animal trainer, before I went to train horses.

584
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:34,300
It was very easy to train it.

585
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:38,700
Consort, it's time to take your medicine.

586
00:34:39,061 --> 00:34:41,208
It will not taste good if it gets cold.

587
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,500
I have to go back to take my medicine.

588
00:34:45,052 --> 00:34:46,142
I was not able to stay long.

589
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,700
Since you were in the rain,

590
00:34:50,967 --> 00:34:53,356
it would be good for you to have hot soup.

591
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,900
Goodbye, Consort.

592
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,800
Keep the albizia flowers.

593
00:35:11,138 --> 00:35:12,109
Yes.

594
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:15,100
That was bizzare.

595
00:35:15,477 --> 00:35:20,356
I was reminded of the night on Ling-Yun mountain, when I saw that huge cat.

596
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:21,800
It was really scary.

597
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:24,200
Are you okay?

598
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:28,000
Yes. She was just using the cat to play with us.

599
00:35:33,100 --> 00:35:34,000
I think

600
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:38,700
the soy bean is delicious.

601
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:41,100
They make it regularly.

602
00:35:41,393 --> 00:35:43,223
I don't find anything special in it.

603
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,800
You like special things.

604
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:47,700
That's why you went to House of Broken Jade?

605
00:35:47,912 --> 00:35:48,836
Are you jealous?

606
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:51,800
I am happy for you.

607
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,700
I was not looking for something special.

608
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:56,600
I hadn't been visitng Consort Hui.

609
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:58,800
Therefore, I felt sorry towards her.

610
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:01,900
Moreover, Mother always urged me

611
00:36:02,158 --> 00:36:03,890
to visit her.

612
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:08,200
But in the end, she still has prejudices against me,

613
00:36:08,258 --> 00:36:09,348
so I just left.

614
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:11,900
How could you do that?

615
00:36:12,393 --> 00:36:13,847
You have to apologize to her.

616
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,400
I had the same thought.

617
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:19,000
But she chased me away, saying she had a cold,

618
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:21,100
when I went to see her today.

619
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,800
Then,

620
00:36:23,343 --> 00:36:25,647
you should go visit Consort An.

621
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:28,000
I wonder why

622
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:31,500
I couldn't bear to leave her

623
00:36:31,822 --> 00:36:33,187
when I went there.

624
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:37,200
Now I don't care about her, even when I haven't gone for a long time.

625
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:40,500
Consort An has her own specialties.

626
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:43,700
Bureau of Astronomy said that Consort An is not auspicious.

627
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,300
Although you are not afraid of it,

628
00:36:47,100 --> 00:36:49,000
you have a shadow in your heart.

629
00:36:49,615 --> 00:36:51,364
Go and visit her after some time.

630
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:53,200
Oh.

631
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:57,700
I am here to tell you something.

632
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:58,800
What is it?

633
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:02,000
The people in the palace are malevolent.

634
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:04,500
I can't tolerate them.

635
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,300
Why do you say so?

636
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,900
You will be angry as well, if I tell you about it.

637
00:37:12,100 --> 00:37:13,100
I have heard

638
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:16,200
worse things than what you have heard.

639
00:37:17,700 --> 00:37:21,000
Since I am not angry about it, there's no need for you to be.

640
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:25,300
I am just afraid you might feel bad.

641
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,700
Since you know about it now,

642
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,700
I no longer feel bad about it.

643
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:33,300
Since you said it is intolerable to you,

644
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:35,700
you don't have to care about it.

645
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:44,100
Zhen-Huan, I only thought you were tender.

646
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:49,800
Now I see you are also calm and deliberate.

647
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:51,800
Many people

648
00:37:52,091 --> 00:37:54,551
will be involved.

649
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:57,400
I have a request.

650
00:37:57,900 --> 00:37:59,800
No matter what you hear from anyone,

651
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:02,191
Don't be angry.

652
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,000
Don't punish them for it.

653
00:38:05,503 --> 00:38:06,391
Alright.

654
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,400
Today is the 15th of the month.

655
00:38:08,592 --> 00:38:10,591
You have to go have dinner with the Empress.

656
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:13,400
Go early. Don't keep her waiting.

657
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:19,200
These are the new dishes I ordered the kitchen to prepare.

658
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:21,900
Have a try.

659
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:34,800
Well,

660
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:37,700
They hold a candle to the dishes at Consort Xi's.

661
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,600
She is pregnant now.

662
00:38:39,834 --> 00:38:42,643
Of course she needs to pay more attention to what she eats.

663
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:45,100
It is tiring for her to be pregnant.

664
00:38:45,426 --> 00:38:47,197
Therefore, she has no appetite.

665
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:50,000
She won't eat the food unless it looks good.

666
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:52,800
Everybody says the baby

667
00:38:52,962 --> 00:38:55,318
of Consort Xi is different.

668
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:58,502
Her stomach is bigger.

669
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:02,900
It is right that we be careful with the baby.

670
00:39:04,103 --> 00:39:05,354
Why do you say that?

671
00:39:07,093 --> 00:39:08,947
Although I am sick,

672
00:39:08,997 --> 00:39:11,486
I hear many rumors.

673
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:13,700
Are you worrying about the rumors

674
00:39:13,759 --> 00:39:17,816
in the palace that never stop?

675
00:39:18,592 --> 00:39:21,893
It is useless to waste your energy

676
00:39:21,972 --> 00:39:24,238
to think about them.

677
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:27,900
Your body was never healthy.

678
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:32,600
Consort Duan and Consort Jing will host the harem for you.

679
00:39:32,989 --> 00:39:35,993
Why do you care about the rumors,

680
00:39:36,158 --> 00:39:37,841
when they don't care about them?

681
00:39:40,439 --> 00:39:42,718
Alright. I am full.

682
00:39:44,600 --> 00:39:46,700
Where are you going?

683
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:50,000
I am going back to Hall of Mental Cultivation,

684
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:52,350
to mark documents.

										

 
 


   
 

  
   
 
 


 

										